import Head from 'next/head'

import '../styles/index.scss'
import Nav from './nav'

function MyApp({ Component, pageProps }) {
    return (
        <React.Fragment>
            <Head>
                <title>Coffee Demo</title>
                <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
            </Head>
            <Nav />
            <Component {...pageProps} />
        </React.Fragment>
    )
}

export default MyApp
